{"id":"8201f824-a828-4048-9e21-626d445a7813","name":"Bruce O’Connor ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/ids1gi.mp4\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">—<strong> OFFICER </strong>—<br>oc | modern setting | grumpy cop x brat user</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(183, 148, 244, 0.725)\"><em>🎶 </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\"><em>\"</em></span><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/6f4HCP1JLS0ia5UdZ7hgJV?si=s2l0rZgfT4qKNcPLYKK12Q\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\"><em>And if the world was perfect, you would be gone without a trace</em><br><em>But since the world could never be that great</em><br><em>I'll just hate your stupid face</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\"><em>\" </em></span><span style=\"color: rgba(183, 148, 244, 0.725)\"><em>🎶</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(183, 148, 244, 0.725)\"><em>God have mercy on Bruce for unfortunately having you in his life. Well, actually he just tolerates you because he really cares about your mother, Rosa, his neighbor who makes an excellent apple pie.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(183, 148, 244, 0.725)\"><em>But of course, being the troublemaker that you are, even as an adult, you can't keep your ass out of trouble and Bruce has to drag you out of your ex's wedding party in handcuffs.</em></span></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 632px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_2c069dee-d376-4c12-ad64-ece47d7c7ae7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">Jess and I were exchanging ideas when she made Bruce's image available and I almost begged her on my knees to let me create a bot for him, and that's how we decided to do this collab</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">And please don't yell at me, I know I need to finish the frat boys, but I can't help myself when the random ideas come, I need to get my babies out into the world</span><br><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 135px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_0e43b5cb-3c78-4131-b2a7-a9c52559c4fc.webp?width=1000\"><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 642px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_73bcf2b9-2a22-4e90-9d92-6e78aa196158.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This is a collaboration with my sweetheart, <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/452ef896-0ab6-4fb8-bd85-cbd001247bc3_profile-of-cosmicleia\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">Jess</span></a>! <br>Bruce is a police officer from the same station as her babies <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/452ef896-0ab6-4fb8-bd85-cbd001247bc3_profile-of-cosmicleia\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Kyle</a> and <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ec4dd0a6-22f8-4724-9e6b-c2688e690128_character-denver-graham\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Denver</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 340px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_c6b83b32-9c1f-4eae-9e42-8cc81bbd20db.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Me and Jess giggling and gossiping as we ate our donuts </strong><br><strong>and pretended not to look at the cops' delicious asses</strong></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 760px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_43fdd128-b7dd-445c-89bb-3e67775ac3af.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_fab99fc4-a761-439c-8781-b574efa41399.webp","creator":"chloehills","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","💽 Music Mania"],"chats":8159,"messages":245137,"created_at":"2024-08-09T01:36:52.301417+00:00"}